---
// Features.astro - 주요 기능 소개 컴포넌트
---

<section class="py-20 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
    <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center text-gray-800 mb-2">주요 기능</h2>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-12">
      TTSG 프로젝트는 다양한 기능을 통합적으로 제공합니다
    </p>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <div
        class="bg-blue-50 rounded-xl p-8 shadow-md transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-lg"
      >
        <div
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-100 to-indigo-100 mb-6"
        >
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            width="24"
            height="24"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="2"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            class="text-blue-600"
            ><path
              d="M18 3a3 3 0 0 0-3 3v12a3 3 0 0 0 3 3 3 3 0 0 0 3-3 3 3 0 0 0-3-3H6a3 3 0 0 0-3 3 3 3 0 0 0 3 3 3 3 0 0 0 3-3V6a3 3 0 0 0-3-3 3 3 0 0 0-3 3 3 3 0 0 0 3 3h12a3 3 0 0 0 3-3 3 3 0 0 0-3-3z"
            ></path></svg
          >
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">블로그</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
          최신 동향과 정보를 블로그 형태로 쉽게 공유하고 토론하세요. 카테고리와 태그를 통한 효율적인
          콘텐츠 관리를 경험해보세요.
        </p>
        <a
          href="/blog"
          class="inline-flex items-center text-blue-600 font-semibold hover:text-blue-700 transition-all duration-300 group"
        >
          자세히 보기
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            width="20"
            height="20"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="2"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            class="ml-2 group-hover:ml-3 transition-all duration-300"
            ><path d="M5 12h14"></path><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"></path></svg
          >
        </a>
      </div>

      <div
        class="bg-blue-50 rounded-xl p-8 shadow-md transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-lg"
      >
        <div
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-100 to-indigo-100 mb-6"
        >
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            width="24"
            height="24"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="2"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            class="text-blue-600"
            ><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle><path d="M9.09 9a3 3 0 0 1 5.83 1c0 2-3 3-3 3"
            ></path><path d="M12 17h.01"></path></svg
          >
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">위키</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
          공동 작업을 통한 지식 구축 및 관리가 가능한 위키 시스템을 활용하세요. 버전 관리와 변경
          내역 추적을 지원합니다.
        </p>
        <a
          href="/wiki"
          class="inline-flex items-center text-blue-600 font-semibold hover:text-blue-700 transition-all duration-300 group"
        >
          자세히 보기
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            width="20"
            height="20"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="2"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            class="ml-2 group-hover:ml-3 transition-all duration-300"
            ><path d="M5 12h14"></path><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"></path></svg
          >
        </a>
      </div>

      <div
        class="bg-blue-50 rounded-xl p-8 shadow-md transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-lg"
      >
        <div
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-100 to-indigo-100 mb-6"
        >
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            width="24"
            height="24"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="2"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            class="text-blue-600"
            ><rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2" ry="2"></rect><path d="M8 21h8"
            ></path><path d="M12 17v4"></path></svg
          >
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">앱</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
          사용자 맞춤형 대시보드와 데이터 시각화 도구를 통해 정보를 효과적으로 분석하고 관리할 수
          있습니다.
        </p>
        <a
          href="/app"
          class="inline-flex items-center text-blue-600 font-semibold hover:text-blue-700 transition-all duration-300 group"
        >
          자세히 보기
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            width="20"
            height="20"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="2"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            class="ml-2 group-hover:ml-3 transition-all duration-300"
            ><path d="M5 12h14"></path><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"></path></svg
          >
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
